Due to the development of disruptive, resource-intensive, and uncontrollable technologies alongside nuclear fallout, drought, overpopulation, climate change, and other human behaviors the end of the world is approaching fast.
Thanks to huge advances in technology, a spaceship built for this very purpose is ready to shuttle the entire human population of Earth to a nearby planet.
This spaceship has limited spots and no room to falsely admit non-humans. To earn their spot, citizens interested in boarding the spaceship must demonstrate their humanness in a world laden with machines and AI.
You are in charge of administering a series of questions to determine who will be admitted onto the spaceship.
Because time is running out, there is only time to talk with each candidate briefly and determine their fate.
Choose wisely, the future of humanity is on the line!
